Class SubTypeSet

  • Object
    • SubTypeSet

  • public class SubTypeSet
extends Object
    A set of classes. This data structure additionally allows for efficient answers to queries about can-be-used-as (Reflection.canBeUsedAs(Class,Class)) relationships.
